OL,3,CGovernment reportedly considering ban
OL,4,Con smoking in pub gardens
OL,6,FRestrictions could be tightened on
OL,7,Fsmoking in public places, including
OL,8,Fbans in pub gardens and outdoor
OL,9,Frestaurants
OL,11,FSmoking in pub gardens could be banned
OL,12,Funder plans to be set out by
OL,13,Fministers, according to leaked
OL,14,Fdocuments.
OL,16,FThe government is reportedly
OL,17,Fconsidering introducing harsher
OL,18,Frestrictions to crack down on tobacco
OL,19,Fproducts.
