OL,3,CGovernment reportedly considering ban
OL,4,Con smoking in pub gardens
OL,6,FOutdoor restaurants, areas outside
OL,7,Fnightclubs and pavements by
OL,8,Funiversities and hospitals are some of
OL,9,Fthe places which could be included
OL,10,Funder the plans, according to
OL,11,Fdocuments seen by The Sun.
OL,13,FSpaces outside football stadiums and
OL,14,Fsmall parks could also see a smoking
OL,15,Fban.
OL,17,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,18,Fspokesperson said: "We do not comment
OL,19,Fon leaks. Smoking claims 80,000 lives
OL,20,Fa year, puts huge pressure on our NHS,
OL,21,Fand costs taxpayers billions.
